title: Iron Ore Shipments, Total for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1889-1915 (2)--Original Data, 1911-1937 (3)--Original Data, 1930-1939. Data Include Beneficiated Ore; Esclude Ore For Paint (Which Is Included In Production Figures) And Manganiferrous Ore Containing Over Five Percent Manganese. Source: U.S. Bureau Of Mines, Minerals Yearbook, 1935-1940.

This NBER data series a01194c appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
